posts.text:
5 Early Release 
In an effort to make new research available as quickly as possible, CDN publishes manuscripts online almost immediately after acceptance. These early release articles are the authors' accepted manuscripts, prior to copyediting, proofreading, and composition. Final versions will be published 4-5 weeks after acceptance, on a continuous basis, and will be available on the Recent Research page. The American Society for Nutrition (ASN) is a non-profit organization dedicated to bringing together the world's top researchers, clinical nutritionists and industry to advance our knowledge and application of nutrition for the sake of humans and animals. Our focus ranges from the most critical details of research and application to the broadest applications in society, in the U.S. and around the world. 
For more information about ASN, please visit www.nutrition.org
